project_descr: Supporting the Electoral Commission of Zambia to prepare for the Tripartite elections in 2006, including development of a roadmap for the elections, establishment of a voter register and implementation of a civic and voter education programme

outputs.output_descr: Supporting the Electoral Commission of Zambia and other GRZ Departments to prepare for the Tripartite elections in 2006. A roadmap for the implementation of the 2006 election was established, the voter register was put in place and a civic and voter education programme was implemented.
